     <a href="/careers" class="inline-flex items-center mt-0 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-blue-700 focus:z-10 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-100 focus:text-blue-700 ">Join Backplane <svg class="w-3 h-3 ms-2 rtl:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 14 10">
       <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"/></svg></a>
    </p>
  
    </div>   -->

   
    </div>
 

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Community
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Backplane is a community-driven project, built by engineers for engineers. It's Open, Free, and our ambition is to develop the Cloud Abstraction API to be the tool in every organisations toolbox for their multi-cloud journeys and donate the project to the Cloud Native Compute Foundation.
  
   
      </p>

 
 
   </div>

   <Community />
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
